<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF806A3FF8269F2D16BFB1E2" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF806A3FF8269F2D16BFB1E2" blockId="123.[2008,2603,2301,2729]" lastBlockId="123.[1395,2602,2735,3478]" pageId="123" pageNumber="881">
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF806A3FF8269F2D1609B2A7" box="[2010,2057,2420,2453]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="123" pageNumber="881">See</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FF7E59F2D16A6B2A7" baseAuthorityName="Peters" baseAuthorityYear="1870" box="[2073,2214,2420,2453]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="egregius">L. egregius</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FF7479F2D17AAB2A7" authorityName="Hall &amp; Jones" authorityYear="1961" box="[2235,2474,2420,2453]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insularis">Lasiurus insularis</taxonomicName>
was first described as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FF6969FFD1423B28F" authorityName="H. Allen" authorityYear="1862" box="[2410,2595,2468,2493]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedius">L. intermedius</taxonomicName>
, and its taxonomic status has been debated over the years. Restriction-enzyme analysis of mtDNA and recent molecular studies based on mtDNA and nDNA showed that 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FF8269C381670B1B0" authorityName="Hall &amp; Jones" authorityYear="1961" box="[2010,2160,2657,2690]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insularis">L. insularis</taxonomicName>
differs enough from 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FF65D9C381610B19B" authorityName="H. Allen" authorityYear="1862" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedius">L. intermedius</taxonomicName>
, and it was elevated to a distinct species. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FFA469CF618A5B1E2" authorityName="Hall &amp; Jones" authorityYear="1961" box="[1466,1701,2735,2768]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="insularis">Lasiurus insularis</taxonomicName>
is in the Yellow Bat group. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF806A3FFA899C8F16C8B1C5" box="[1397,2248,2774,2807]" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FF806A3FFA899C8F16C8B1C5" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398378" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398378" box="[1397,2248,2774,2807]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398378/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" targetBox="[1395,1986,2308,2722]" targetPageId="123">
